    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Demo Version Specifications</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play up to <strong>Stage 1-8</strong> of the main game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Saving is not available</strong> in the Demo version, and progress <strong>cannot be carried over</strong> to the full game.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A One-Button Jump Action Game!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick to play, quick to clear! If you don't have much time but still want a thrilling experience, <strong>JETMAN</strong> is the game for you!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Jump and Defeat Enemies!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The height of your jump varies depending on how long you hold the button. Time your jumps carefully to land the perfect attack! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868340/extras/b902d4c055f3fed80e1fffcfce7c316b.poster.avif?t=1772186805\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868340/extras/b902d4c055f3fed80e1fffcfce7c316b.webm?t=1772186805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868340/extras/b902d4c055f3fed80e1fffcfce7c316b.mp4?t=1772186805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Over 50 Unique Enemies!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wide variety of enemies with distinct appearances and movement patterns await. Observe their behaviors and strategize for an efficient victory! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868340/extras/931e6348bc0671ded1248a99e352e83d.poster.avif?t=1772186805\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868340/extras/931e6348bc0671ded1248a99e352e83d.webm?t=1772186805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868340/extras/931e6348bc0671ded1248a99e352e83d.mp4?t=1772186805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Your Character with JP (Junk Points)!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the points earned in battles to power up your character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you <strong>boost your attack</strong> or <strong>reinforce your defense</strong>? The choice is yours! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868340/extras/8c0dbddc7e5e6c37a3485a84eea13aeb.poster.avif?t=1772186805\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868340/extras/8c0dbddc7e5e6c37a3485a84eea13aeb.webm?t=1772186805\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868340/extras/8c0dbddc7e5e6c37a3485a84eea13aeb.mp4?t=1772186805\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Story Full of Colorful Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created by Dr. Ark to stop the evil <strong>Violets Organization</strong>, Jet—a half-android hero—takes center stage in this action-packed adventure! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1868340/extras/7603fce78ff36cff0a23cc8142f7192a.avif?t=1772186805\" width=320 height=180 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Post-Game Content</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clearing the main story unlocks <strong>special game modes</strong>. Dive deeper into the world of <strong>JETMAN</strong> and enjoy the full experience!</p>",
